{"tid":2417131,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"林作: 致曾志偉先生 建議TVB買下「臨終之戰」直播權。","createTime":"2021-02-21T15:13:27.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-22T06:16:51.000Z","uid":318316,"like":6,"dislike":27,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"9e1626c2e324ea351db96678225d7c0de86fa943","tid":2417131,"uid":318316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T15:13:27.000Z","msg":"致TVB 副總經理曾志偉先生：<br />\n本人將同終生提議，建議TVB買下「臨終之戰」直播權。<br />\n既然閣下負責綜藝節目，希望改革，一洗頹勢，咁就讓無綫回歸當年本質，為大家帶來真正嘅娛樂吧。我能夠一舉將收視推上當年高峰。因為本人代表的，就是現今時下的娛樂。<br />\n唯一問題，係唔知你OK唔OK台上搞出人命。畢竟，目前業餘足球圈瘋傳，話林作，其實係個好勁嘅運動員，重錘出擊，後果自負。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5WkhF7i.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5WkhF7i.jpg&h=abb5713f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"680889e2a1ce7e424651d30d7f54abdb2be6d385","tid":2417131,"uid":37666,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T19:33:26.000Z","msg":"佢真係想紅想到痴線"},{"pid":"e2ef09845f5a6f40a5b2c22d70a362c842209f67","tid":2417131,"uid":293376,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T19:40:29.000Z","msg":"呢條友係咪陳雲個私生仔"},{"pid":"d2cf2c94ba7aef13e7cd178fd5b2c7740bc3d55d","tid":2417131,"uid":99973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T05:46:29.000Z","msg":"痴撚線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d3af94fa489f9ed6d59a403dd30a372ce60eb90","tid":2417131,"uid":257974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T06:04:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8f53a6ca46f60c847a23144c163dc7a1e69f087","tid":2417131,"uid":57862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T06:05:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji